@startuml
title UC11 - Notificar Aluno por E-mail

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

queue "RabbitMQ
moedas.email" as MQ
control "EmailConsumer" as Consumer
control "TransacaoRepository" as TransRepo
control "ProfessorRepository" as ProfRepo
control "AlunoRepository" as AlunoRepo
control "EmailService" as EmailService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
collections "Gmail SMTP" as SMTP
actor Aluno as A
actor Professor as P

MQ -> Consumer: Entrega EnvioMoedasEvent
activate Consumer
Consumer -> TransRepo: findById(transacaoId)
activate TransRepo
TransRepo -> DB: SELECT transacao
activate DB
DB --> TransRepo: Transação
deactivate DB
TransRepo --> Consumer: Transação
deactivate TransRepo

Consumer -> ProfRepo: findById(professorId)
activate ProfRepo
ProfRepo -> DB: SELECT professor
activate DB
DB --> ProfRepo: Professor
deactivate DB
ProfRepo --> Consumer: Professor
deactivate ProfRepo

Consumer -> AlunoRepo: findById(alunoId)
activate AlunoRepo
AlunoRepo -> DB: SELECT aluno
activate DB
DB --> AlunoRepo: Aluno
deactivate DB
AlunoRepo --> Consumer: Aluno
deactivate AlunoRepo

Consumer -> EmailService: enviar e-mails de confirmação
activate EmailService
EmailService -> SMTP: E-mail para professor
activate SMTP
SMTP --> EmailService: OK
deactivate SMTP
EmailService -> SMTP: E-mail para aluno
activate SMTP
SMTP --> EmailService: OK
deactivate SMTP
EmailService --> Consumer: E-mails enviados
deactivate EmailService
Consumer --> MQ: ACK da mensagem
deactivate Consumer

SMTP --> P: Recebe confirmação de envio
SMTP --> A: Recebe aviso de moedas
@enduml
